Package: simplified.forecaster
Title: Evaluating a Simplified Forecast Model in Comparison to the ECDC Forecasting Hub Ensemble
Description: This repository contains the documentation, results, and code of a
   project evaluating a simplified forecasting model in comparison the ECDC
   forecasting hub ensemble. See the documentation for further details. 
